[I] A EXIF tag and data access library

[T] The EXIF library allows you to parse an EXIF file and read the data from
[T] those tags. Most digital cameras produce EXIF files, which are JPEG files
[T] with extra tags that contain information about the image.

[U] https://libexif.sourceforge.net

